Gym Workouts: 60 - 90 sec rest between sets
1. Squats: Reps - 10,12 for 2 sets 2. Leg Extensions: Reps - 12 for 1 set 3. Leg Curls: Reps - 12 for 1 set 4. Standing Calf Raises: Reps - 10,12 for 2 sets 5. Bench Press: Reps - 10,12 for 2 sets 6. Flyes: Reps - 12 for 1 set 7. Pushdown: Reps - 12 for 1 set

Bodyweight Strength: 30 - 60 sec rest inbetween sets
1. Spidermans x 8 side - 3 sets 2. Inchworms x 8 side - 3 sets 3. Pinwheel shinbox x 8 side - 3 sets 4. Thread the needle x 8 side - 3 sets 5. Repeat 2x
